data.description: Space, comfort, and convenience await you at this 2 story home in Carolina Forest's "Avalon" subdivision.  This property offers a modern and welcoming design, with a spacious two-car garage that provides ample parking and storage space.  On the first floor you'll find an open concept layout, including a kitchen with stainless steel appliances, a cozy living room, a dining area, and a guest bathroom.  Heading to the second floor, you'll find the primary bedroom with an ensuite bathroom and walk-in closet, as well as two or more additional bedrooms and a shared bathroom. This layout provides privacy and convenience for the whole family.  Avalon is a nice  family community with an impressive waterfall entrance that welcomes you home.  Being in the Carolina forest area, it's close to shopping, dining, beach attractions, and the best schools in Horry County, South Carolina.  The 11-acre community center features a swimming pool, baseball diamond, soccer field, basketball court, volleyball court, fishing pond, childrens playground, covered picnic pavillion with picnic tables and charcoal grills, and much more.   DON'T DELAY - COME SEE ME TODAY!
